ng\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkJCmTiL.png&h=8ea487df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://club.commonhealth.com.tw/article/1321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fclub.commonhealth.com.tw%2Farticle%2F1321&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLuxR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=02ce0ea9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://club.commonhealth.com.tw/article/1321</a>"},{"pid":"39f1ccd23426fdcadd9115eeb32769af86b58e10","tid":2040374,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:16:54.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLuxR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=a8cc0eb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精由腎儲藏，而精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，症狀都唔同，以下為最常見：<br />\n早洩，變樣哀，猥瑣，臉色灰暗，自卑冇自信、腰痛<br />\n腦力下降，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n戒為良藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLuxR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=272fcdef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a><br />\n戒J 前後對比圖<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.noj1314.258club.com/forumdisplay.php?fid=63\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.noj1314.258club.com%2Fforumdisplay.php%3Ffid%3D63&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLuxR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=afeec79e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.noj1314.258club.com/forumdisplay.php?fid=63</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ需知： <br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ後３個月內症狀加重／加深屬正常，係戒斷反應<br />\n<br />\n身體恢復過程並唔係直線上升，而係好似過山車咁上下移動，會不斷由壞轉好，好轉壞<br />\n但隨著時間既增長，身體會慢慢恢復，症狀慢慢消失<br />\n<br />\n夢